1
00:00:00,310 --> 00:00:01,570
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,570 --> 00:00:03,310
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:05,180
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,610 --> 00:00:09,580
I did not kill Kim Myung Hui.

5
00:00:10,850 --> 00:00:12,350
The one who killed Kim Myung Hui...

6
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:16,450
was Kim Dan Hui, who wanted
to steal her twin sister's life.

7
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:24,460
It was...

8
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:27,130
that woman right there.

9
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:30,070
(Exposing Chairman Park Tae Ho
as a Murderer...)

10
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:34,210
That's just a baseless,
one-sided accusation.

11
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:39,440
Do you think I came here
without any evidence?

12
00:00:44,250 --> 00:00:45,520
(Exposing Chairman Park Tae Ho
as a Murderer...)

13
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,820
(and Revealing
Kim Dan Hui's Identity)

14
00:00:56,630 --> 00:00:59,230
Do you think
I haven't thought of that?

15
00:00:59,830 --> 00:01:01,400
Even if we're going
to kill Kim Dan Hui,

16
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:04,340
we need to do it differently.

17
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:05,970
Differently?

18
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:10,610
I'll frame Kim Dan Hui
as Kim Myung Hui's...

19
00:01:12,540 --> 00:01:14,280
killer.

20
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:16,580
What?

21
00:01:16,710 --> 00:01:19,280
She wanted to steal
her twin sister's life...

22
00:01:19,350 --> 00:01:21,090
after the sister found
a rich husband.

23
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:25,660
So she killed her sister
and spent 30 years...

24
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,530
living under her name.

25
00:01:28,790 --> 00:01:32,400
Don't you think the public
would eat that story up?

26
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,200
As for you,

27
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:39,900
you'll be the one...

28
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:45,140
to solve the mystery
from 30 years ago.

29
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:50,220
By revealing that Kim Myung Hui
and Kim Dan Hui were twins,

30
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:52,080
I...

31
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:55,520
will be cleared of the suspicion
of being a murderer.

32
00:01:56,450 --> 00:01:59,460
And you'll be
the competent police officer...

33
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:01,260
who solved a cold case.

34
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:04,660
It's a pretty picture, isn't it?

35
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:09,500
In that case...

36
00:02:11,570 --> 00:02:13,140
We'll have to create
some evidence...

37
00:02:14,010 --> 00:02:15,710
that can fool everyone, won't we?

38
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,890
This woman, Kim Dan Hui,

39
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:32,620
claims that Chairman Park Tae Ho
strangled Kim Myung Hui.

40
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:33,730
However,

41
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:35,460
thirty years ago,

42
00:02:35,890 --> 00:02:37,960
the cause of death
on the autopsy report...

43
00:02:40,330 --> 00:02:42,570
was death by poisoning.

44
00:02:42,570 --> 00:02:43,640
What's going on?

45
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,700
He's saying Kim Dan Hui
is the murderer?

46
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,800
What?

47
00:02:48,110 --> 00:02:49,110
What is this?

48
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,310
That's ridiculous!

49
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,880
(Exposing Chairman Park Tae Ho
as a Murderer...)

50
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:03,820
You didn't even see my sister's body
30 years ago.

51
00:03:04,290 --> 00:03:05,460
How can a police officer...

52
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,630
try to fool people
with fabricated evidence?

53
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,360
When the truth comes out,

54
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,860
your career as a police officer
will be over.

55
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,000
Ms. Kim, please stop lying.

56
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:20,040
Didn't you fabricate the recording
of Chairman Park Tae Ho as well?

57
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:21,570
Ms. Kim,

58
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,010
did you really murder Kim Myung Hui?

59
00:03:23,270 --> 00:03:24,780
Did you fabricate the recording
of Chairman Park Tae Ho?

60
00:03:25,010 --> 00:03:27,010
Were you jealous
of your twin sister's life?

61
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:28,750
Are you framing
Chairman Park Tae Ho?

62
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:30,920
- Is it true?
- Please comment.

63
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,250
The evidence was fabricated,
wasn't it?

64
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:37,560
- Today's evidence... Is it fake?
- It's fabricated, isn't it?

65
00:03:38,290 --> 00:03:40,660
The recording wasn't fabricated.

66
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:43,730
A professional analysis
will prove it.

67
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:46,930
Yes, I was also there and heard it
when it was being recorded.

68
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:50,700
Excuse me, members of the press.

69
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:53,870
A current member of the police force
is exposing the truth,

70
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:56,740
bringing forward evidence
from 30 years ago.

71
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,010
As for who's telling the truth...

72
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,980
I'll let you be the judge.

73
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:07,620
You murdered your twin sister,
didn't you?

74
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,750
- Didn't you?
- Are you innocent?

75
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,690
Did you really murder
your twin sister?

76
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:15,060
Are you innocent?

77
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:18,900
- Is it true?
- Is it a fact?

78
00:04:19,030 --> 00:04:21,470
You murdered her, didn't you?

79
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,200
(Adele Group
Emergency Press Conference)

80
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:28,440
I can't believe Park Tae Ho
would pull a move like this.

81
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:30,210
I know.

82
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:33,140
He's even more cunning
than I thought.

83
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,950
Still, it's just a suspicion
for now.

84
00:04:36,650 --> 00:04:39,380
People will believe you over Father,

85
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:40,890
so don't worry too much.

86
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,720
All right.

87
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:46,790
- Murderer.
- Murderer.

88
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:47,860
You murderer.

89
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:49,230
- Mother!
- You're a murderer.

90
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:52,400
- Murderer.
- Mother!

91
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:56,300
- You're Kim Dan Hui, right?
- Stop it.

92
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:58,000
The murderer
who killed her twin sister.

93
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:00,670
How could you do that?
Are you a psychopath?

94
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:03,210
How could you kill your sister
and steal her life?

95
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,680
I heard you tried to make
the chairman of Adele Group...

96
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,880
divorce his wife.

97
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:09,650
- You're just horrible.
- What do you think you're doing?

98
00:05:09,710 --> 00:05:10,720
Film it.

99
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,680
Don't speak so lightly
when you don't even know the truth.

100
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:15,520
- Film it.
- Don't. Put your cameras away.

101
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:17,020
- Stop filming.
- I said stop filming.

102
00:05:17,090 --> 00:05:19,220
- Stop filming.
- Keep filming.

103
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,360
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

104
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:24,100
Yes, sir.

105
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:27,500
I've created the scene
you asked for.

106
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,000
Send those photos
to the board right now.

107
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,740
And push them on the fact
that Kim Dan Hui can't be...

108
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,910
a candidate for chairman.

109
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,170
Yes, I understand.

110
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,610
Put your cameras away.

111
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:43,250
- I said stop filming.
- Park Tae Ho is behind this mob.

112
00:05:45,150 --> 00:05:46,950
- Mother.
- Ms. Kim.

113
00:05:47,050 --> 00:05:48,450
- Where are you going?
- She's a murderer.

114
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:49,520
Murderer!

115
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:03,530
Are you really that happy?

116
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,640
I mean, after living together
for 30 years,

117
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:08,910
you'd think
there'd be some affection.

118
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,510
Affection?

119
00:06:13,710 --> 00:06:16,780
If she had any affection,
would she have been so hell-bent...

120
00:06:17,450 --> 00:06:19,020
on taking me down?

121
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:26,360
She was literally just
an empty shell of Kim Myung Hui.

122
00:06:27,890 --> 00:06:29,130
That's all she was.

123
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:37,540
She lived a pampered life
for over 30 years thanks to me,

124
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:43,910
and yet she had the audacity
to come after the great Park Tae Ho.

125
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:48,850
This is a slap on the wrist,
if you ask me.

126
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:51,780
There.

127
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:05,200
This tastes especially good today.
Go on, eat.

128
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,670
I'm hungry
for something other than this.

129
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:11,240
You've already been paid,

130
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,770
and you're asking for more?

131
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:17,840
This whole affair
has exposed me completely.

132
00:07:18,710 --> 00:07:19,710
Since it's come to this,

133
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,650
I should be the one...

134
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:24,750
to watch your back properly,
for a long, long time.

135
00:07:24,850 --> 00:07:26,520
Hey, just you wait.

136
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,550
Once I'm back in my position
as chairman,

137
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:32,160
I'll make sure that "deputy" tag...

138
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,030
comes off your name.

139
00:07:35,130 --> 00:07:36,490
That's not going to happen.

140
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:45,340
To get reinstated as chairman.

141
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:48,540
You framed me for murder
just for that?

142
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:51,780
How dare you exploit
my sister's death like that?

143
00:07:53,340 --> 00:07:55,450
I may not be able
to put you in prison,

144
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,780
but I won't let you get
your position back.

145
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:03,720
Kim Dan Hui,
what can you possibly do?

146
00:08:04,490 --> 00:08:06,490
If you're not my woman,

147
00:08:07,230 --> 00:08:09,560
you're nothing in the Adele Group.

148
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,200
Your sister, who clung to my money,

149
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,600
and you, running around
trying to get revenge,

150
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,600
are both the same.

151
00:08:17,570 --> 00:08:19,070
You are nothing...

152
00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:21,540
but parasites beneath my feet.

153
00:08:23,370 --> 00:08:25,210
What...

154
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:28,510
Hey.

155
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:33,220
Kim Dan Hui, you!

156
00:08:35,250 --> 00:08:37,090
I can take you insulting me,

157
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:40,260
but I won't tolerate you
insulting my sister,

158
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,160
who died at your hands.

159
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:47,160
I pity my sister for having
truly loved a beast like you.

160
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:49,700
I can't ever forgive you for that.

161
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,240
If you insult my sister
one more time,

162
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:58,410
I'll tear that mouth apart.

163
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:03,180
Kim Dan Hui!

164
00:09:07,650 --> 00:09:08,650
A police officer...

165
00:09:10,450 --> 00:09:11,960
fabricates evidence?

166
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,490
About that...

167
00:09:16,490 --> 00:09:17,500
Hey.

168
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:22,030
Do you have any idea
how expensive this suit is?

169
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,100
Are you crazy?

170
00:09:24,770 --> 00:09:26,740
You shouldn't be so shocked.

171
00:09:27,610 --> 00:09:31,080
I haven't even started
on the crazy yet.

172
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:35,980
Fine. Bring it on.

173
00:09:36,850 --> 00:09:39,780
Frame me for murder
and try to destroy me,

174
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,890
but I'll never break.

175
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,960
I'll fight to the very end...

176
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:50,490
and I'll destroy you both.

177
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,070
Why you...

178
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:11,780
Kim Dan Hui...

179
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:18,020
Park Tae Ho, that shameless man.

180
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:21,160
Man? Calling him human
is a waste of breath.

181
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:24,330
How could he be so cruel to Dan Hui?

182
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,530
It's because
of the upcoming chairman election.

183
00:10:27,330 --> 00:10:29,900
He was afraid my mother would win,

184
00:10:29,970 --> 00:10:31,440
so he framed her for murder.

185
00:10:31,970 --> 00:10:35,210
If she can't prove her innocence,
people will continue to suspect her.

186
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:37,140
That can't happen.

187
00:10:37,210 --> 00:10:40,180
What if I stepped up
and testified...

188
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:41,680
to Dan Hui's innocence?

189
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,380
Who'd believe you?

190
00:10:44,050 --> 00:10:46,050
They'll just think you're biased
because you're her friend.

191
00:10:47,950 --> 00:10:51,160
We just have to prove
our evidence is genuine.

192
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:53,020
I'll start
by getting the recording...

193
00:10:53,090 --> 00:10:55,130
and bloodstain evidence
authenticated.

194
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:57,960
Park Tae Ho and Detective Yun.

195
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:03,430
I'll expose the fact
that they are lying.

196
00:11:08,810 --> 00:11:11,280
The recording wasn't fabricated.

197
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:14,410
A professional analysis
will prove it.

198
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:17,650
Yes, I was also there
and heard it when...

199
00:11:18,380 --> 00:11:19,450
(Kim Dan Hui,
Suspect in Sister's Murder)

200
00:11:19,450 --> 00:11:20,450
(Press Conference in Shambles)

201
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,560
Park Hyun Jun.

202
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:34,670
What happened between you and Chloe?

203
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,400
It seems you're siding
with the chairman.

204
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:40,910
Did you break up with Chloe?

205
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:43,940
What is it?

206
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,840
Are you here to gloat
about being right all along?

207
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,210
Want me to describe
what it feels like...

208
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:51,620
to be betrayed by Min Jun and Chloe?

209
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:55,290
Anyway, you broke up, right?

210
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,360
Does that mean...

211
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,060
you have a chance?

212
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,960
A chance?

213
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:14,470
A chance to take Chloe's old spot...

214
00:12:16,170 --> 00:12:17,410
right next to me.

215
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,440
What?

216
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,520
No can do.

217
00:12:27,950 --> 00:12:31,590
I can't stand seeing
that hopeful look on your face.

218
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:35,390
It makes my stomach turn
every time I see it.

219
00:12:56,410 --> 00:12:57,410
Hyun Jun.

220
00:12:58,250 --> 00:13:00,480
You saw Kim Dan Hui's
press conference, right?

221
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:04,660
Park Tae Ho paid her back
for everything, with interest.

222
00:13:05,090 --> 00:13:07,260
It doesn't look like
she'll become chairman, does it?

223
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,390
I told you.

224
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:12,060
Father is trying to return
to his position as chairman.

225
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,370
It means he still doesn't
approve of me.

226
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:17,270
He has no intention
of handing over his position.

227
00:13:17,330 --> 00:13:20,200
Don't worry about that.
Just as you asked,

228
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:22,470
I've been in contact
with the directors.

229
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:24,540
No, that's not enough.

230
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,550
If we want to pressure Father,
we need to find...

231
00:13:28,210 --> 00:13:29,710
another angle.

232
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:36,290
(Adele)

233
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:40,390
If I were President Kim,

234
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,830
I'd have completely broken down
from the injustice.

235
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,400
What's public opinion like?

236
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:49,600
Between Park Tae Ho and Kim Dan Hui,
who do they think did it?

237
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:51,070
It's about fifty-fifty.

238
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:54,370
Those who believe the recording
say Chairman Park did it,

239
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:57,410
and those who trust the police
say President Kim did it.

240
00:13:57,980 --> 00:14:01,610
People love to talk
when it's not their problem.

241
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,320
What are you doing here?

242
00:14:10,390 --> 00:14:12,490
Did you come here
to take your anger out on me too?

243
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:14,490
I wanted to have a quiet word
with you.

244
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:17,430
What? A quiet word?

245
00:14:18,330 --> 00:14:19,330
The two of us?

246
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:39,250
You said I poisoned your sister,
and that I'm a murderer.

247
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:42,420
What could you possibly want
to discuss with a murderer?

248
00:14:44,090 --> 00:14:47,420
That's right.
For 30 years, to me, you were...

249
00:14:48,190 --> 00:14:49,790
a murderer and my enemy.

250
00:14:50,490 --> 00:14:52,400
If it meant
getting my revenge on you,

251
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:56,530
I was resolved to do
whatever it took.

252
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:58,840
Living as my sister,

253
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:01,840
I could even endure
being Park Tae Ho's woman.

254
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:05,740
I didn't even realize
I was blinded by revenge.

255
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:07,980
Oh Jung Ran.

256
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:11,080
My entire life was focused on you.

257
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,550
What is this?

258
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:17,120
Why are you here
telling me your sob story?

259
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,960
Because you and I are
in the same boat.

260
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:22,060
What?

261
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:24,560
Deceived by Park Tae Ho,

262
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:28,470
we spent 30 years being used by him
and fighting a pointless battle.

263
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:30,770
If it weren't for him,

264
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:33,600
You and I...

265
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,270
would've lived
completely different lives.

266
00:15:37,210 --> 00:15:38,780
I want to talk about...

267
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:41,650
this deep injustice
and feeling of emptiness,

268
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,820
and the only person
who could truly understand...

269
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,050
is, of all people,

270
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:54,330
Oh Jung Ran,
the woman I hated to death.

271
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:57,130
I realized
only you could understand me.

272
00:15:59,730 --> 00:16:04,440
I want to bring that man,
Park Tae Ho, crashing down.

273
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:08,140
Don't you feel the same way?

274
00:16:08,770 --> 00:16:11,710
So? What are you trying to say?

275
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:16,010
I can't let him reclaim his position
as chairman of Adele Group.

276
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:19,220
Testify that he killed my sister,

277
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:23,250
and that he and Detective Yun
are lying.

278
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:30,360
You want me to testify for you?

279
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:34,470
When it's obvious you'll take over
as chairman of Adele Group?

280
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:36,670
Don't tell me...

281
00:16:37,230 --> 00:16:39,170
you actually came here
expecting me to agree?

282
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,240
Still,

283
00:16:42,410 --> 00:16:43,740
I held out hope,

284
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:46,510
so I came here on the off chance.

285
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:50,110
Then you can leave,
thinking it was what you expected.

286
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,550
Right.

287
00:16:53,020 --> 00:16:56,920
Park Tae Ho is telling me
to fire your son from the company,

288
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:58,720
but I'm holding off for now.

289
00:16:59,020 --> 00:17:01,590
So make sure you
keep your mouth shut...

290
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,560
about Hyun Jun's secret.

291
00:17:24,110 --> 00:17:26,120
But I do agree with you
on one thing.

292
00:17:26,950 --> 00:17:30,320
I won't let Park Tae Ho take back
the chairman's seat either.

293
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:31,690
Just you watch.

294
00:17:33,060 --> 00:17:34,560
That's the one and only thing...

295
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:36,960
we agree on.

296
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,460
Fine.

297
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:41,970
Even that's good enough for me.

298
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:56,410
I had hoped,

299
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:59,520
but Oh Jung Ran has no intention
of testifying.

300
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,850
She only wants
to make Hyun Jun the chairman...

301
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:03,220
instead of Park Tae Ho.

302
00:18:03,290 --> 00:18:07,930
Then we must find another way
to expose Park Tae Ho's lies.

303
00:18:10,090 --> 00:18:11,090
(DNA Analysis Center)

304
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:16,470
First,
I had our evidence authenticated.

305
00:18:16,770 --> 00:18:20,300
Now that we've confirmed
the evidence is genuine,

306
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:23,640
please deliver this to Moon Tae Jin,
the largest shareholder.

307
00:18:23,840 --> 00:18:27,280
Tell him not to fall for
Park Tae Ho's lies and to trust us.

308
00:18:27,340 --> 00:18:30,080
We'll send it to all directors.

309
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:31,450
All right.

310
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:33,720
I will relay the message.

311
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,090
And...

312
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:38,260
I'd like to put someone
on Detective Yun.

313
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,920
I want to expose the deal...

314
00:18:41,230 --> 00:18:42,560
between Park Tae Ho and him.

315
00:18:42,630 --> 00:18:44,960
You want to catch them
exchanging money?

316
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:47,260
Like when we caught Park Cheol Su?

317
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:50,930
If we can pull it off,
it's the best way.

318
00:18:51,840 --> 00:18:55,370
We'll need to create a situation
that forces Detective Yun...

319
00:18:55,370 --> 00:18:56,910
to demand money.

320
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,140
Wait.

321
00:18:58,710 --> 00:19:00,610
What if I report
the warehouse incident...

322
00:19:00,610 --> 00:19:01,880
to the police?

323
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:04,650
Park Tae Ho might reach out
to Detective Yun,

324
00:19:05,180 --> 00:19:06,750
and they could end up making a deal.

325
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:07,890
In that case,

326
00:19:08,490 --> 00:19:11,790
I'll put a tail on Detective Yun.

327
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,510
I saw the press conference.

328
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:31,440
It looks like
you've handled your issues,

329
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:34,110
but what are you going to do
about Chloe?

330
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:36,710
Chloe?

331
00:19:36,910 --> 00:19:38,950
Now that everyone knows
her memory is fine,

332
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:40,580
she's been openly threatening me.

333
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:44,150
She's making a fuss about reporting
the warehouse incident,

334
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:45,660
and I'm worried.

335
00:19:52,130 --> 00:19:55,570
Sir, Chloe went to the police
about the warehouse incident.

336
00:19:56,670 --> 00:19:58,240
See? I was right.

337
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,440
You need to step in
and handle this right away.

338
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:02,240
Contact Detective Yun...

339
00:20:02,970 --> 00:20:04,310
and tell him to handle it.

340
00:20:04,310 --> 00:20:05,510
Understood, sir.

341
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:08,280
Don't think this is over.

342
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:11,110
Keep an eye on Chloe
and report back to me.

343
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:13,350
Yes, I'll do that.

344
00:20:23,330 --> 00:20:24,330
What's going on?

345
00:20:24,460 --> 00:20:27,430
- Haven't you heard from the board?
- Heard what?

346
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:30,400
They sent an authentication report
to the directors.

347
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:34,170
It confirms that all
the murder evidence is authentic.

348
00:20:35,770 --> 00:20:39,140
Then that would put Park Tae Ho
in a corner.

349
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:42,350
That's why I was hoping
we could push him even further.

350
00:20:43,950 --> 00:20:45,650
Are you suggesting
we blackmail Park Tae Ho?

351
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:49,090
It seems like a good opportunity.
Got any ideas?

352
00:20:49,150 --> 00:20:52,220
Always. Blackmail is my specialty.

353
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:56,690
Besides, I just got
the perfect excuse.

354
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:27,790
Kim Dan Hui came to see me today.

355
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:30,090
Kim Dan Hui? What for?

356
00:21:30,690 --> 00:21:34,730
She asked me to testify
that you were lying.

357
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:41,370
If I testify,
you won't just be a murderer.

358
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:44,040
You'll also be the piece of trash...

359
00:21:44,410 --> 00:21:46,610
who framed an innocent victim,
Kim Dan Hui.

360
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:51,250
So does that mean
Kim Dan Hui becomes chairman?

361
00:21:52,780 --> 00:21:53,880
What did you just say?

362
00:21:54,020 --> 00:21:55,650
There's only one way...

363
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,720
to shut me up.

364
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:00,920
In your stead,

365
00:22:02,130 --> 00:22:03,630
I'll be taking the chairman's seat.

366
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:08,700
Are you two ganging up on me?

367
00:22:08,970 --> 00:22:10,500
I'd expect as much from Oh Jung Ran,

368
00:22:10,630 --> 00:22:13,340
but what do you think you're doing,
Park Hyun Jun?

369
00:22:13,570 --> 00:22:14,570
Let me see.

370
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:17,440
Aren't I behaving
how your son should?

371
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:19,640
What?

372
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:22,350
To be chairman,
you have to be cold-hearted.

373
00:22:23,050 --> 00:22:25,580
You told me to put the company
before family.

374
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,450
And for the sake of the company,

375
00:22:28,550 --> 00:22:30,790
it'd be better for me
to take the seat than you.

376
00:22:30,850 --> 00:22:31,860
Shut it!

377
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:35,860
Not while I'm alive.
Over my dead body.

378
00:22:48,770 --> 00:22:51,240
Hello? Director Seo,

379
00:22:51,980 --> 00:22:54,140
gather the directors right now.

380
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:56,650
Call any reporters you know too.

381
00:22:57,810 --> 00:23:00,150
I'm thinking of testifying.

382
00:23:00,950 --> 00:23:02,690
I'm going to tell them...

383
00:23:03,050 --> 00:23:06,690
whether Kim Dan Hui or Park Tae Ho
killed Kim Myung Hui.

384
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,590
Hey, give me that.

385
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:12,960
Do you have a death wish?

386
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:15,800
Go ahead and try to kill me.

387
00:23:16,600 --> 00:23:18,700
Then our Hyun Jun
will tell the world...

388
00:23:19,670 --> 00:23:22,840
that you killed Kim Myung Hui,
and that you killed me too.

389
00:23:22,870 --> 00:23:23,940
What?

390
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:27,140
- Oh Jung Ran.
- Father!

391
00:23:29,010 --> 00:23:32,420
Father, I'm your son.

392
00:23:32,780 --> 00:23:35,450
Becoming chairman doesn't mean
I'm stealing the company from you.

393
00:23:36,090 --> 00:23:37,590
Please, just trust me.

394
00:23:38,220 --> 00:23:42,160
Exactly. Hyun Jun is the only child
you have left who is backing you.

395
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:45,060
Instead of being humiliated...

396
00:23:45,130 --> 00:23:47,160
and losing the company
to Kim Dan Hui,

397
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:50,000
hand it over
to our only son, Hyun Jun.

398
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:55,370
Use your phone
to call Director Seo...

399
00:23:55,710 --> 00:23:57,810
and declare that
you're handing it over to Hyun Jun.

400
00:23:59,940 --> 00:24:02,380
Darn it.

401
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:09,790
You think stepping down as chairman
means I've lost my power?

402
00:24:10,050 --> 00:24:13,190
If I expose the Munhwadang incident
I covered up,

403
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:16,630
you'll be seen as a murderer too,

404
00:24:17,360 --> 00:24:19,230
just like Kim Dan Hui!

405
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:24,100
If you get it,
then shut up and stay out of it.

406
00:24:24,700 --> 00:24:27,300
. There's only one chairman
of Adele Group, and it's me.

407
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:31,510
No one can take that away from me!

408
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,510
The nerve...

409
00:24:41,050 --> 00:24:42,050
Well,

410
00:24:43,150 --> 00:24:45,560
I didn't expect him to agree
right away.

411
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:49,230
If we threaten him a few more times,

412
00:24:49,630 --> 00:24:52,430
he'll have no choice
but to hand it over to you.

413
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:14,220
Every single one of them...

414
00:25:15,090 --> 00:25:16,950
is desperately trying
to drag me down.

415
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:27,500
Sir, Detective Yun
is demanding money again.

416
00:25:30,430 --> 00:25:31,970
Money-mad, is he?

417
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:35,470
How hard can it be to handle
one little accusation?

418
00:25:36,210 --> 00:25:37,540
Get him in here right now!

419
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:39,040
Well...

420
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:42,050
He's refusing to come,
saying he isn't in the mood...

421
00:25:42,050 --> 00:25:43,510
to get drenched like last time.

422
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:44,980
He also said there are...

423
00:25:44,980 --> 00:25:46,420
more eyes on him
since the press conference,

424
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:48,320
so if you need to talk,

425
00:25:48,790 --> 00:25:50,350
you should meet somewhere private.

426
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:56,830
He helps me with one thing,

427
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,730
and he has already gotten
this arrogant?

428
00:26:00,230 --> 00:26:01,230
That punk.

429
00:26:01,800 --> 00:26:03,700
Get me a meeting
with Detective Yun right away!

430
00:26:04,300 --> 00:26:05,300
Yes, sir.

431
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,620
You punk.

432
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:22,520
Darn it.
What do you think you're doing?

433
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:24,020
Thirty years ago,

434
00:26:24,650 --> 00:26:27,720
you got a beating
for being arrogant with me.

435
00:26:29,290 --> 00:26:30,290
Remember that?

436
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:33,430
I'm not the same person
I used to be.

437
00:26:33,730 --> 00:26:36,270
How dare you strike
a high-ranking police official?

438
00:26:37,230 --> 00:26:38,970
How dare I?

439
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,940
Just because you helped me out,

440
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:45,540
don't fool yourself into thinking
you have something on me.

441
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,780
Every time you take my money,

442
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:50,980
it goes right into my ledger.

443
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:54,280
Give it here.

444
00:26:57,690 --> 00:26:59,490
Don't ever get cocky with me again.

445
00:26:59,860 --> 00:27:02,030
Just handle the task
you've been given.

446
00:27:21,910 --> 00:27:25,220
These are the photos Mrs. Han sent.
What do you think?

447
00:27:26,380 --> 00:27:29,250
You can clearly see
the bag of money.

448
00:27:29,350 --> 00:27:30,390
You're right.

449
00:27:30,850 --> 00:27:33,390
We can prove that money
was exchanged between them.

450
00:27:33,690 --> 00:27:35,790
Let's figure out the best way
to use this.

451
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,440
Yes, Director.

452
00:27:48,570 --> 00:27:50,240
Please carefully review
the authentication report...

453
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,510
we sent over.

454
00:27:52,010 --> 00:27:54,110
The killer in that case
from 30 years ago...

455
00:27:54,410 --> 00:27:56,080
It's Chairman Park Tae Ho.

456
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:00,650
Yes, I'll be in touch.

457
00:28:12,130 --> 00:28:13,130
Mr. Song.

458
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:22,010
I came to talk to you
about Hyun Jun.

459
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:26,840
Right, I think I know
what this is about.

460
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,250
You kept Hyun Jun's secret...

461
00:28:29,850 --> 00:28:32,820
and dealt with Choi Yu Na
who was tormenting him,

462
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:33,880
so I trusted you.

463
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:38,390
Did you conspire with Chloe
to deceive and use him?

464
00:28:39,420 --> 00:28:42,590
That's not what happened.
It's a misunderstanding.

465
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:45,260
A misunderstanding?

466
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,800
Even this misunderstanding...

467
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:55,070
was all because
of Hyun Jun's secret.

468
00:28:55,170 --> 00:28:56,640
A number of things...

469
00:28:57,370 --> 00:29:00,580
seem to have hurt his feelings.

470
00:29:00,840 --> 00:29:04,380
To be honest, being worried
is another reason I came to you.

471
00:29:06,020 --> 00:29:07,320
I'm worried that Hyun Jun...

472
00:29:07,650 --> 00:29:11,590
will become a monster, just like
Jung Ran and Chairman Park.

473
00:29:13,290 --> 00:29:16,590
He's so set on becoming
the chairman of Adele Group...

474
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:18,460
that he's even blackmailing
Chairman Park.

475
00:29:19,730 --> 00:29:21,930
I don't know
if we should let this continue.

476
00:29:22,430 --> 00:29:23,570
Blackmail?

477
00:29:28,970 --> 00:29:29,970
Blackmail?

478
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:33,410
Hyun Jun blackmailed Park Tae Ho
for the chairman position?

479
00:29:34,410 --> 00:29:37,350
I think the secret is making him
even more desperate,

480
00:29:37,780 --> 00:29:41,550
and I wonder if he's pushing himself
too hard because of us.

481
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:45,760
You haven't seen him
since that day, have you?

482
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:47,720
He won't take my calls.

483
00:29:48,660 --> 00:29:50,760
Still, I really wish
you'd try and see him.

484
00:29:50,860 --> 00:29:52,430
I talked to him,

485
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:54,600
but it only made things worse.

486
00:29:55,900 --> 00:29:59,040
I think you're the only one
who can calm Hyun Jun down.

487
00:30:01,070 --> 00:30:03,510
Okay. I'll try to talk to him.

488
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,780
(Adele)

489
00:30:11,950 --> 00:30:13,520
Can we talk for a minute?

490
00:30:14,120 --> 00:30:16,450
I don't want to hear your excuses.
Get out.

491
00:30:17,950 --> 00:30:19,890
Can't you just hear me out?

492
00:30:23,090 --> 00:30:24,090
Park Hyun Jun.

493
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,260
Hyun Jun.

494
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:31,130
I came here to apologize.

495
00:30:37,510 --> 00:30:39,640
I'm sorry for giving you
the wrong impression.

496
00:30:40,610 --> 00:30:43,210
The idea that I ignored you because
you're not Park Tae Ho's son,

497
00:30:43,780 --> 00:30:45,950
or betrayed you because you're
no longer useful to my revenge,

498
00:30:46,620 --> 00:30:47,720
is absurd.

499
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:51,220
I thought you wanted to hide it,

500
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:52,960
so I pretended not to know.

501
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:56,390
I really had no idea it would cause
this kind of misunderstanding.

502
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,460
That's not the only thing you hid.

503
00:31:00,560 --> 00:31:01,560
At the time,

504
00:31:03,070 --> 00:31:05,970
I couldn't carelessly reveal
Ms. Kim's secret.

505
00:31:07,670 --> 00:31:08,670
I thought...

506
00:31:09,410 --> 00:31:11,840
your mother was the one
who murdered Kim Myung Hui.

507
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:15,180
That kept me from telling you.

508
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:21,650
So it wasn't just about my father.

509
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:24,650
You were targeting my mother,

510
00:31:25,220 --> 00:31:27,690
plotting something,
and until the very end...

511
00:31:29,390 --> 00:31:31,290
- That's...
- You sided...

512
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:35,470
with Kim Dan Hui, who was hell-bent
on destroying my mom,

513
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:39,170
and you were too busy hiding it
to even ask me if I was okay.

514
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:43,110
Kim Dan Hui mattered more to you
than I did.

515
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:45,170
To you,
revenge always took priority!

516
00:31:46,810 --> 00:31:48,280
Meanwhile, you were my entire world.

517
00:31:50,410 --> 00:31:51,410
Baek Jin Ju,

518
00:31:51,950 --> 00:31:53,780
you're the only one I see.

519
00:31:55,950 --> 00:31:56,950
But you...

520
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,930
You don't respect me at all.

521
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:11,070
Park Hyun Jun.

522
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:15,610
What did he just say?

523
00:32:17,570 --> 00:32:18,570
Baek Jin Ju?

524
00:32:46,040 --> 00:32:48,970
(Pearl in Red)

525
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:51,510
Kim Dan Hui is still the problem.

526
00:32:51,670 --> 00:32:54,980
What if she reveals the secret
just to one-up Hyun Jun?

527
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:58,550
I should've bought her silence
by promising to testify.

528
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:00,580
Now that Choi Yu Na knows,

529
00:33:00,850 --> 00:33:02,050
Father will find out soon.

530
00:33:02,050 --> 00:33:04,250
Please protect Jin Ju
from any fallout.

531
00:33:04,620 --> 00:33:06,320
Handle it yourself.

532
00:33:06,690 --> 00:33:08,760
I don't have the time
to protect someone...

533
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:10,590
who betrayed me.

534
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:14,530
Don't take this any further.
You have a good life as Chloe.

535
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,530
A good life?

536
00:33:17,100 --> 00:33:19,100
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
